data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. FINANCING INCENTIVE! Significant loan savings using the seller's preferred lender. Offering 1-0 Temporary Rate Buydown which gets you *1 PERCENT* below market rate for a year and until March 31st, you will also receive an appraisal credit up to $600.    Welcome to your own piece of paradise at 40237 Trotter Ln, Dade City, FL 33525! Nestled on a generous .69-acre lot, this charming property boasts all the features you need for an idyllic staycation retreat: Expansive Layout, Intentional Indoor & Exterior Spaces to Entertain, TWO Overside RV & Boat Parking Pads & a Beautiful Lot with Mature Trees.     Step into your personal oasis, where you'll find a heated pool and a screened-in lanai, ideal for relaxation and entertaining. But that's not all – there's a brand-new wooden pergola that offers a picturesque setting for hosting friends and family gatherings. With ample space for grilling and outdoor seating.Here's your chance to experience the tranquility of a vast backyard shaded by beautiful trees, complete with an inviting arbor, perfect for enjoying outdoor fires during those crisp, starry nights.    This well-maintained and remodeled home, offering nearly 2,000 square feet of living space, features 4 spacious bedrooms and 2 beautifully renovated bathrooms with an incredible split floor plan lay out providing the ultimate entertaining spaces to host  but also providing privacy for your family or guests.     The heart of this home is the great room, where a wood-burning fireplace sets the perfect ambiance for cozy evenings. A separate dining room adds a touch of elegance, while the completely renovated and open kitchen steals the show. This kitchen boasts a center island, with beautiful gray granite countertops, and modern cabinets, making it the perfect space for culinary creations and family gatherings.      No need to worry about essential home improvements: all the windows are vinyl, double paned & the roof is only 6 years old, ensuring your peace of mind for years to come.    Privacy is paramount, with a fully fenced backyard and a large remote-controlled electric gate that offers ample access to the garage, backyard for boat parking or the RV port. It gets better - ANOTHER parking pad on the Right side of the home. Bring the RV & The Boat! Best of all, there are no deed restrictions or HOA, giving you the freedom to make this property your own.    Only 10 Minutes to Charming & Expanding Downtown Dade City with Breweries, Curated Restaurants (The Wine Library & Greendoor Cafe), Coffee Shops! Less than 20 Minutes to Brand New development Mirada (Publix, Mirada Lagoon), Less than 25 Minutes to Wesley Chapel, Less than 35 Minutes to Lakeland, & 45 Minutest to Downtown Tampa!     Don't miss your chance to experience the ultimate staycation at 40237 Trotter Ln. This is more than just a home; it's a retreat, a sanctuary, and a place to create cherished memories with loved ones. Welcome home! Don't miss the virtual tour.
